## Critical Rules
- ALWAYS use `logging.getLogger(__name__)` to create loggers
- NEVER use print statements for logging
- NEVER use emojis in log messages
- Use hybrid format: readable message + key=value pairs for data
- Include service= to identify the component
- Include error=, count=, status= for relevant data
- Quote values that contain spaces or special characters
- Use f-strings for dynamic content in messages